comments: Adebayo (MIA) makes marginal contact to Randle's (NYK) body during his shooting motion on the driving shot attempt.
Gibson (NYK) slightly extends his arms into Johnson (MIA), but does not dislodge him from his rebounding position.
Johnson (MIA) makes contact to Gibson's (NYK) arm during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
Johnson (MIA) places a hand/arm to the front of Randle (NYK) on the drive and the contact affects his SQBR.
Bullock (NYK) makes marginal contact with Butler (MIA) during his drive to the basket.
Butler (MIA) makes contact with the ball while it is still inside the imaginary cylinder above the rim.
Butler (MIA) makes marginal contact to the body of Barrett (NYK) as he releases the pass.
Dragic (MIA) makes marginal contact to Randle's (NYK) arm during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.

Replay review of the shooting foul called on Bullock (NYK) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Bullock moves into Butler's (MIA) space and makes contact to his leg during his jump shooting motion.
Johnson (MIA) commits a take foul on Barrett (NYK).
Gibson (NYK) absorbs the contact from Butler (MIA) during the driving shot attempt.
Dragic (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Gibson (NYK) and absorbs the contact.
Adebayo (MIA) commits a take foul on Barrett (NYK).
Adebayo (MIA) briefly engages and disengages with Gibson (NYK) during the rebound.
Bullock (NYK) makes incidental contact with Adebayo (MIA) as he attempts to steal the inbound pass.
